Mr. Barber, over here!

151
00:11:22,975 --> 00:11:24,619
Mr. Barber,
do you have any comment?

152
00:11:24,643 --> 00:11:26,403
Give us a
little room here, please.

153
00:11:26,436 --> 00:11:28,146
Give us a little room here.

