00:35:33,967 --> 00:35:36,757
And all of this bullying, it upset Jacob.

572
00:35:37,429 --> 00:35:39,389
- Yeah, of course.
- Did it make him angry?

573
00:35:41,141 --> 00:35:42,731
Not so much in front of Ben, but...

574
00:35:44,102 --> 00:35:46,812
privately, he'd go off on how
