site Jake was into called The Cut Up Room.

597
00:36:57,176 --> 00:37:00,006
By "messed up," I'm assuming
you mean pornographic.

598
00:37:00,095 --> 00:37:03,885
Yeah, but, it's not really
so much about sex.

599
00:37:03,974 --> 00:37:07,354
More violence. Like, really graphic stuff.

600
00:37:07,436 --> 00:37:09,186
Are there stories on this site?

601
00:37:10,147 --> 00:37:14,937
Yeah, people post all kinds
of stuff. Photos, videos, stories.

602
00:37:15,027 --> 00:37:17,607
And do you know if
Jacob posted any stories?

603
00:37:19,239 --> 00:37:20,819
He did, yeah.

604
00:37:20,908 --> 00:37:22,738
He called them Job stories.

605
00:37:23,869 --> 00:37:25,079
Job stories?

606
00:37:25,162 --> 00:37:28,672
Yeah, you know, like his initials. J-O-B?

607
00:37:29,791 --> 00:37:31,461
That was his screen name on there.

608
00:37:32,586 --> 00:37:33,796
What do you know about this?

609
00:37:33,879 --> 00:37:35,339
Not enough. You got to shut it down.

610
00:37:35,422 --> 00:37:38,842
And did Job post a story
about the murder of Ben Rifkin?

611
00:37:39,426 --> 00:37:40,466
Yes.

612
00:37:44,139 --> 00:37:46,139
Commonwealth
moves to enter into evidence...

613
00:37:46,183 --> 00:37:47,393
Objection.

614
00:37:47,476 --> 00:37:48,726
Your Honor, may we approach?

615
00:37:48,810 --> 00:37:50,850
Settle down, please.

616
00:37:52,648 --> 00:37:55,148
Respectfully, Your
Honor, we ask to approach.

