that's hardly the Commonwealth's fault.

620
00:38:08,747 --> 00:38:10,077
What's this about, Jacob?

621
00:38:10,916 --> 00:38:12,036
Jacob?

622
00:38:34,523 --> 00:38:36,733
Your Honor, I need
to confer with my client.

623
00:38:36,817 --> 00:38:38,437
All right, go ahead.

624
00:38:42,406 --> 00:38:43,906
I'm gonna ask your patience

625
00:38:43,991 --> 00:38:47,581
while I allow defense counselor
a moment to confer with her client.

626
00:38:50,497 --> 00:38:54,247
He's going to allow it unless our position
is that Jacob didn't write the story.

627
00:38:54,710 --> 00:38:56,938
- Then that's our plan...
- They know that he wrote it, Andy.

628
00:38:56,962 --> 00:38:58,462
They've got an IP address.

629
00:39:00,465 --> 00:39:01,795
Jacob.

630
00:39:07,139 --> 00:39:10,849
