00:42:32,052 --> 00:42:34,142
I didn't know it would be a big deal.

671
00:42:40,394 --> 00:42:41,404
Did you do it?

672
00:42:44,565 --> 00:42:46,225
Just tell me. Did you kill him?

673
00:42:56,910 --> 00:42:57,950
No.

674
00:43:04,960 --> 00:43:05,960
No.

675
00:43:25,814 --> 00:43:29,114
I could ask the judge to issue a
bench warrant for Matt McGrath.

676
00:43:29,735 --> 00:43:33,105
