witness holed up in Florida.

677
00:43:34,323 --> 00:43:36,583
We don't have a choice.
We gotta go straight at Patz.

678
00:43:36,658 --> 00:43:38,303
Yeah, his subpoena was served this morning.

679
00:43:38,327 --> 00:43:41,247
