No.

692
00:44:17,616 --> 00:44:20,616
I don't wanna bring her into
this. It's my trial. I'm saying no.

693
00:44:21,870 --> 00:44:23,870
Sorry, but you don't get
a say in this anymore.

694
00:44:26,792 --> 00:44:28,382
Not after today.

695
00:44:42,266 --> 00:44:44,726
I'll get into
it first thing tomorrow.

